  "original_title": "Court imposes travel ban on 21 Galle Face protesters",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Court imposes travel ban on 21 Galle Face protesters",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Fort Magistrate's Court today issued an order preventing 21 Galle Face protesters from leaving the country.",
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage issued this order following a request made by Fort Police over an investigation against the protesters for allegedly causing public nuisance after blocking the main entrances to the Presidential Secretariat.",
        "The Fort Police informed court that they have received intelligence reports regarding the possibility of protesters leaving the country. They sought an order preventing the protesters from leaving the country via Katunayake and Mattala Airports.",
        "Accordingly, the Fort Magistrate issued travel ban on Ven. Wigoda Watte Kashyapa Thera, M.G. Thisara Anuradha, L.N.D. Perera, P.B.M. Ramesh Indika, R.A. Rajapaksa, A.A. Cyril Manatunga, W.P. Isuru Warnakula, Roshan Ali Danis Ali, T.C. Chandimal Gamage, D.R.S. Bentara Arachchi, N.M. Thaufiq, M. Casim, Nilantha Samith Fernando, Koralage Bandula Prabhath, H.M.T.G. Menika, Sameera Madhushanka Siriwardena, Sudath Lakshman, M.R. Charuka, D.P. Chathurika Sarojani, J. Nilantha and M. Nishanthi. (Lakmal Sooriyagoda)"
      ],
